1. Introduction

Style Desk (“we”, “our”, or “the App”) is an application intended for a specific group of invited users.
Access to the App is restricted and requires an account that is created and managed by an administrator.

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect personal data when you use the App.

2. Information We Collect

We collect only the information necessary to provide the App’s functionality, including:

Email address

User identifier

Account role and status

App usage data (such as login events or feature usage)

We do not collect sensitive personal data.

3. How We Use Information

Collected information is used solely to:

Authenticate and authorize users

Manage user access and roles

Provide and improve app functionality

Ensure security and prevent unauthorized access

We do not sell, rent, or share personal data for advertising or marketing purposes.

4. Account Management

User accounts are not created automatically.

All accounts are:

Created by an administrator

Activated or deactivated by an administrator

Restricted to authorized users only

Users without an active account cannot access the App.

5. Account Deletion

Users may request deletion of their account and associated data by contacting the administrator or the support email listed below.

Upon request:

The account is permanently deleted

Associated personal data is removed in accordance with applicable laws

6. Data Sharing

We do not share personal data with third parties except when required to operate the App (for example, backend or infrastructure services) or when legally required.

7. Data Security

We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect user data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.

8. Children’s Privacy

The App is not intended for use by children. We do not knowingly collect data from individuals under the age of 13.

9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Changes will be reflected by updating the “Last updated” date above.

10. Contact Information

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to request account deletion, please contact:

Email: orucbalabey@gmail.com
